benefits:
At Viettel Post, candidates will have the opportunity to work in a dynamic, youthful, and professional environment, accompanied by the following attractive benefits:

1. Compensation and Benefits

Competitive salary based on individual capability and agreement;

Additional allowances for phone expenses and lunch, along with annual company-sponsored vacation trips;

Performance and holiday bonuses awarded on major national and corporate occasions (e.g., April 30th, May 1st, September 2nd, Viettel Group and Corporation founding anniversaries, Gregorian and Lunar New Year);

Opportunities for frequent international business trips, working in a multicultural environment, and directly contributing to the global expansion of Viettel Post’s business network.(For long-term overseas assignments, income will follow a separate compensation scheme applicable to local markets.)

